article.description: — Nika Metskhvarishvili scored 23 points to lead UL Monroe past UT Arlington 62-55 on Saturday.
article.headline: Metskhvarishvili scores 23, UL Monroe defeats UT Arlington
article.linkText: Metskhvarishvili scores 23, UL Monroe defeats UT Arlington
article.story: ARLINGTON, Texas -- — Nika Metskhvarishvili scored 23 points to lead UL Monroe past UT Arlington 62-55 on Saturday. Russell Harrison added 19 points and 13 rebounds for the Warhawks (10-8, 2-4 Sun Belt). Patrick Mwamba had 20 points for the Mavericks (8-9, 4-2). —-
